# GLIDER Documentation

Welcome to the GLIDER documentation. This guide covers everything from installation to advanced plugin development.

## Getting Started

New to GLIDER? Start here:

- **[Installation](docs/getting-started/installation.md)** - System requirements and setup
- **[Quick Start](docs/getting-started/quickstart.md)** - Your first experiment in 5 minutes
- **[Core Concepts](docs/getting-started/concepts.md)** - Understanding GLIDER's architecture

## User Guide

Learn how to use GLIDER effectively:

- **[Builder Mode](docs/user-guide/builder-mode.md)** - Desktop IDE for creating experiments
- **[Runner Mode](docs/user-guide/runner-mode.md)** - Touch-optimized execution dashboard
- **[Hardware Setup](docs/user-guide/hardware-setup.md)** - Connecting Arduino and Raspberry Pi
- **[Creating Experiments](docs/user-guide/creating-experiments.md)** - Working with the node graph
- **[Running Experiments](docs/user-guide/running-experiments.md)** - Execution, monitoring, and control
- **[Data Recording](docs/user-guide/data-recording.md)** - CSV logging and data analysis

## Developer Guide

Extend GLIDER with custom components:

- **[Architecture](docs/developer-guide/architecture.md)** - System design and patterns
- **[Plugin Development](docs/developer-guide/plugin-development.md)** - Creating plugins
- **[Custom Nodes](docs/developer-guide/custom-nodes.md)** - Building flow graph nodes
- **[Custom Drivers](docs/developer-guide/custom-drivers.md)** - Hardware board drivers
- **[Custom Devices](docs/developer-guide/custom-devices.md)** - Device type implementations
- **[Contributing](docs/developer-guide/contributing.md)** - Development setup and guidelines

## API Reference

Complete API documentation:

- **[Core API](docs/api-reference/core.md)** - GliderCore, ExperimentSession, DataRecorder
- **[Hardware API](docs/api-reference/hardware.md)** - HardwareManager, BaseBoard, BaseDevice
- **[Flow API](docs/api-reference/flow.md)** - FlowEngine, GliderNode
- **[Built-in Nodes](docs/api-reference/nodes.md)** - All node types by category
- **[Serialization](docs/api-reference/serialization.md)** - File format and schema
- **[Plugins](docs/api-reference/plugins.md)** - PluginManager API

